text: Colleen Furgeson (born 21 November 1998) is a Marshallese swimmer. She competed in the women's 50 metre freestyle event at the 2016 Summer Olympics, where she ranked 58th with a time of 28.16 seconds. She did not advance to the semifinals. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Marshallese female swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of the Marshall Islands Category:Swimmers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Female freestyle swimmers
